        <title>Git的rebase的拓展</title>
        <link>https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 06 Sep 2022 19:35:41 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/cover.png" alt="Featured image of post Git的rebase的拓展" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;简介&#34;&gt;简介&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最近在看&lt;strong&gt;raywenderlich&lt;/strong&gt;家的&lt;em&gt;Advanced Git&lt;/em&gt;，&lt;strong&gt;raywenderlich&lt;/strong&gt;的出的书，我一直挺喜欢的。这本&lt;em&gt;Advanced Git&lt;/em&gt;第三章讲了一些关于&lt;code&gt;rebase&lt;/code&gt;的拓展操作让我觉得非常的有用。所以在这里记录了一下。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;提供一个供练习的git库 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/CorrectRoadH/git-practice&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/CorrectRoadH/git-practice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;使用rebase合并commit&#34;&gt;使用rebase合并commit&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如果我们有多个commit时，如果我们想把多个commit合并成一个时&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;git log --oneline --graph&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1094&#34;
	height=&#34;428&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/1_hu8ed5266b39fa5c8ca6ad9323d3248c74_183799_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/1_hu8ed5266b39fa5c8ca6ad9323d3248c74_183799_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;1&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;255&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;613px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;以这个log为例，我们想把commit 2 与 3 合并成一个commit。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我们就需要&lt;code&gt;rebase -i &lt;/code&gt;到2之前的commit，比如这里为&lt;code&gt;git rebase 20f0d49&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后我们就进到这样的一个页面。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1184&#34;
	height=&#34;724&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/2_hu00fb851e40ad9e37c0133d6e39d5feab_382335_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/2_hu00fb851e40ad9e37c0133d6e39d5feab_382335_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;163&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;392px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我们把3的&lt;code&gt;pick&lt;/code&gt;改成&lt;code&gt;squash&lt;/code&gt;或者&lt;code&gt;s&lt;/code&gt;都行，这样3与3的上面那个(2)都会进行合并。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;326&#34;
	height=&#34;240&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/3_hu794b97485123b64ac3c94bef4fe117c2_49112_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/3_hu794b97485123b64ac3c94bef4fe117c2_49112_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;135&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;326px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后退出(esc,:wq)，看到这里应该不会有不会用vim的同学吧。🤔&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在退出vim之后，又会进到另一个vim。在这里编辑2、3所合并的新commit的commit message。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1238&#34;
	height=&#34;1214&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/4_hu447063b46b4231981f15fedfcf00bfa9_588104_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/4_hu447063b46b4231981f15fedfcf00bfa9_588104_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;101&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;244px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在这里，我们直接&lt;code&gt;gg&lt;/code&gt;、&lt;code&gt;dG&lt;/code&gt;，把整个文件清空，然后写上整合2和3的新commit的消息。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/5.png&#34;
	width=&#34;342&#34;
	height=&#34;416&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/5_hu25232beea5695d82ff37fddf9edbdb32_51064_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/5_hu25232beea5695d82ff37fddf9edbdb32_51064_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;82&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;197px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;继续保存退出。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1068&#34;
	height=&#34;324&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/6_hu0946562b36029eca3d4cf6dd70dfcc58_145950_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/6_hu0946562b36029eca3d4cf6dd70dfcc58_145950_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;329&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;791px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;现在我们看git log。合并完成!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/7.png&#34;
	width=&#34;610&#34;
	height=&#34;296&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/7_hu0bb664a9bc1f012f2603a488f98ade41_66219_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/7_hu0bb664a9bc1f012f2603a488f98ade41_66219_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;206&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;494px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;调整commit的顺序&#34;&gt;调整commit的顺序&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/8.png&#34;
	width=&#34;920&#34;
	height=&#34;318&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/8_hu5fa7bcba172a7ccaf53bc2cbadd7b0b8_109582_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/8_hu5fa7bcba172a7ccaf53bc2cbadd7b0b8_109582_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;289&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;694px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我们想把2与3的位置交换的话&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;git rebase -i 1的hash&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后进入VIM&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/9.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1530&#34;
	height=&#34;1756&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/9_hu884f7619fc0eacf315267a498c632eb4_951830_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/9_hu884f7619fc0eacf315267a498c632eb4_951830_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;87&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;209px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;交换你想交换的commit的顺序。(比如可以使用&lt;code&gt;dd&lt;/code&gt;和&lt;code&gt;p&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/10.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1078&#34;
	height=&#34;412&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/10_hua87bbc8fa20a60d8024484da8d89fce8_165879_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/10_hua87bbc8fa20a60d8024484da8d89fce8_165879_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;261&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;627px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后退出vim就可以了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/11.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1604&#34;
	height=&#34;156&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/11_huc0bd84a8b3fd8ac60b60beb707d1f142_60198_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/11_huc0bd84a8b3fd8ac60b60beb707d1f142_60198_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;1028&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;2467px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/12.png&#34;
	width=&#34;580&#34;
	height=&#34;310&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/12_hu3577cb320b5f4c69b7d8ec8253d6f1ce_63988_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/12_hu3577cb320b5f4c69b7d8ec8253d6f1ce_63988_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;187&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;449px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;交换成功!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;重写历史commit的消息&#34;&gt;重写历史commit的消息&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;同上，直接rebase -i进去，然后修改的commit消息。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在你要重写历史的commit之前把&lt;code&gt;pick&lt;/code&gt;改成&lt;code&gt;reword&lt;/code&gt;或者 &lt;code&gt;r&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/13.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1122&#34;
	height=&#34;338&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/13_hu6ddfb6a3828528e183a8dc759215a889_170696_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/13_hu6ddfb6a3828528e183a8dc759215a889_170696_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;331&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;796px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后保存退出vim，接下来进来这里，&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/14.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1716&#34;
	height=&#34;902&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/14_hu08b2afbe9f70b3698d3e6e8c25f3b241_416334_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/14_hu08b2afbe9f70b3698d3e6e8c25f3b241_416334_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;190&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;456px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这里我们可以直接清空，然后把新的 commit 消息写下。然后保存退出就ok了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;删除指定commit&#34;&gt;删除指定commit&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;同上，进入到rebase interact之后，我们把要删的commit前面的pick改成d或者drop之后保存退出就ok了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/15.png&#34;
	width=&#34;340&#34;
	height=&#34;212&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/15_hua139966dc6d814c4d74c998b0cbf4283_35287_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://correctroadh.github.io/p/git%E7%9A%84rebase%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95/15_hua139966dc6d814c4d74c998b0cbf4283_35287_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;2&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;160&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;384px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;总结&#34;&gt;总结&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;rebase通过&lt;code&gt;-i&lt;/code&gt;(interact)提供了大量有用的功能，同时非常的好记、好上手。&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        
